Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止倒退
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前为止 没什么危险的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 破废铁会将鲸乌贼全部消灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.27,0:00:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破废铁 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认栖息于该海域的希迪亚斯已全部歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.07,0:00:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 干得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 把人形机器人全部开出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的宝物是我们的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.67,0:00:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
